Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.31,0:01:03.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.52,0:01:06.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I missed the vital spot! I'll put you at ease--
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.23,0:01:08.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Askeladd...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.27,0:01:12.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanted to be friends with you...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.53,0:01:20.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. Bjorn...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.33,0:01:22.70,Default,,0,0,0,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.75,0:01:25.79,Default,,0,0,0,,You are my only...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.08,0:01:28.21,Default,,0,0,0,,friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.64,0:01:41.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Send me off...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.70,0:02:04.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, then, sorry to keep you waiting, kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.33,0:02:06.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Come.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.59,0:02:13.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll play with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.86,0:03:58.28,Default,,0,0,0,,LONE WOLF
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.37,0:04:09.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.00,0:04:11.54,Default,,0,0,0,,He's acting different than usual.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.88,0:04:18.80,Default,,0,0,0,,So? Who do you think is going to win, prince?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.88,0:04:20.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Want to make a bet?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.80,0:04:22.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't care who wins.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.84,0:04:24.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll stop the duel before someone dies.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.47,0:04:27.76,Default,,0,0,0,,You're no fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.01,0:04:32.89,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't get to see duels \Nbetween such skilled warriors every day.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.10,0:04:38.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, then, which one do you think is stronger?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.78,0:04:43.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Me? Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.45,0:04:48.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess Askeladd. I bet one pound of silver on him.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.16,0:04:50.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not going to make a bet. \NWhy do you think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.91,0:04:55.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Just a feeling. It's his aura.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.46,0:04:59.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Thorfinn defeated you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.71,0:05:01.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Is Askeladd even better than that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.76,0:05:05.34,Default,,0,0,0,,You. Prince. Who do you think I am?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.43,0:05:11.18,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no way that I'm the weakest one \Nout of us three. Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.60,0:05:17.73,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not that simple to tell who's stronger \Nand who's weaker.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.81,0:05:22.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Sometimes you win, and sometimes you lose. \NIt's not easy to rank people. That's the fun part.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.11,0:05:25.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not interested.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.20,0:05:27.91,Default,,0,0,0,,You must be a woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.87,0:05:33.62,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Thorfinn? Come.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.66,0:05:37.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to finish this before the snow gets worse.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.96,0:05:45.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I have no choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.52,0:05:56.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Look. Now, it's easier to attack me, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.77,0:06:00.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Come, boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.83,0:06:17.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.50,0:06:25.17,Default,,0,0,0,,You still don't understand why it turns out like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.02,0:06:45.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I take back what I said just now. \NThis isn't a duel.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.61,0:06:49.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Askeladd knows Thorfinn's habits. \NHe can see through his cover.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.12,0:06:54.91,Default,,0,0,0,,These two must have dueled many times. \NWhat's the reason for the duel?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.99,0:06:58.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know. No one told me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.46,0:07:05.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Unbelievable.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.21,0:07:07.26,Default,,0,0,0,,You never learn, kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.76,0:07:11.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you get full of yourself after you beat Thorkell?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.81,0:07:19.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sick of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.60,0:07:23.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop! That's enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.32,0:07:30.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you think you could beat me \Nwith only one arm?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.49,0:07:36.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.29,0:07:39.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Today, I'm feeling damn good.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.12,0:07:41.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.63,0:07:52.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop. He's passed out.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.34,0:07:53.93,Default,,0,0,0,,You win.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.01,0:07:58.52,Default,,0,0,0,,You're really going to stop them?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.60,0:08:01.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Thorfinn! Hey! Thorfinn!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.23,0:08:12.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you understand? The duel is over.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.82,0:08:14.45,Default,,0,0,0,,You lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.45,0:08:22.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Enough. It's over now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.12,0:08:23.29,Default,,0,0,0,,You bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.37,0:08:25.79,Default,,0,0,0,,You passed out.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.88,0:08:27.54,Default,,0,0,0,,He already delivered the deathblow.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.63,0:08:34.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Start over again once your right arm has healed.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.64,0:08:39.89,Default,,0,0,0,,It will end the same way \Neven after your arm heals.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.97,0:08:42.02,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not because of your wound.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.10,0:08:44.69,Default,,0,0,0,,You're an idiot who loses because he's an idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.48,0:08:49.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Normally, you know how to think while you fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.48,0:08:54.32,Default,,0,0,0,,But once you lose your temper, \Nit all goes to waste.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.45,0:08:59.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I can tell from where you're looking \Nthat you're going after my neck.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.04,0:09:06.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Losing your temper, shouting loudly,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.88,0:09:10.13,Default,,0,0,0,,and waving your sword around \Nis how an idiot fights.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.21,0:09:12.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Unbelievable. Everyone's the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.88,0:09:15.13,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no beauty in it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.72,0:09:19.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Bjorn is right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.51,0:09:22.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I hate warriors.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.31,0:09:27.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Especially Norse warriors, Vikings.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.02,0:09:33.74,Default,,0,0,0,,The first man I ever killed was also a Norse warrior.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.82,0:09:36.36,Default,,0,0,0,,He was not a beautiful man.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.91,0:09:42.66,Default,,0,0,0,,He was my father.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.37,0:09:47.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Kid...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.33,0:09:49.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to tell you something for future reference.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.25,0:09:55.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to tell you how to kill someone you hate.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.48,0:10:10.36,Default,,0,0,0,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.44,0:10:12.90,Default,,0,0,0,,-I'm getting old. \N-Watch out behind you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.53,0:10:20.99,Default,,0,0,0,,My mother was a slave.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.83,0:10:28.50,Default,,0,0,0,,My mother was sick and couldn't work.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.54,0:10:32.84,Default,,0,0,0,,So, ever since I was old enough to remember,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.92,0:10:35.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I was working in the blacksmith's shop and the stable.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.93,0:10:41.43,Default,,0,0,0,,My body was always covered in
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.51,0:10:46.02,Default,,0,0,0,,ash, coal, or horse manure, \Nand was always white or black.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.10,0:10:48.10,Default,,0,0,0,,They gave me the nickname "Askeladd."
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.19,0:10:52.19,Default,,0,0,0,,It means "covered in ash."
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.65,0:10:56.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Olaf has returned!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.78,0:10:59.70,Default,,0,0,0,,He was victorious again!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.91,0:11:08.71,Default,,0,0,0,,My father was from a powerful family in Jutland.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.79,0:11:12.29,Default,,0,0,0,,-Olaf! \N-Welcome back, Olaf!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.38,0:11:15.71,Default,,0,0,0,,He loved booze, women and killing people.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.80,0:11:18.22,Default,,0,0,0,,He was a Viking, \Njust like those you'd find anywhere else.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.38,0:11:24.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard he had lots of kids like me \Nwith random women here and there.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.14,0:11:28.85,Default,,0,0,0,,But he only named the older kids \Nhe had with his legal wife.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.94,0:11:36.48,Default,,0,0,0,,He probably didn't even know \Nwhat his other kids looked like.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.95,0:11:42.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard that my mother
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.57,0:11:45.87,Default,,0,0,0,,was one of my father's favorite slaves \Nwhen she was younger.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.95,0:11:50.87,Default,,0,0,0,,But after she fell ill, he treated her like a dog.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.21,0:11:55.88,Default,,0,0,0,,For me, life had always been hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.96,0:11:59.05,Default,,0,0,0,,But it was different for my mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.22,0:12:08.64,Default,,0,0,0,,My mother often told me about \Nthe hero Artorius, one of our ancestors.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.72,0:12:11.44,Default,,0,0,0,,She told the same story many times.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.15,0:12:15.90,Default,,0,0,0,,The legend was about a general \Nwho protected my mother's homeland
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.98,0:12:19.44,Default,,0,0,0,,from being invaded by savages 500 years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.49,0:12:25.53,Default,,0,0,0,,My mother believed the legend's prophecy \Nthat the hero would be resurrected.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.62,0:12:31.08,Default,,0,0,0,,She believed that he would return \Nto free her from illness and enslavement.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.96,0:12:36.25,Default,,0,0,0,,She kept repeating it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.33,0:12:38.34,Default,,0,0,0,,So, I started to believe it, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.63,0:12:42.05,Default,,0,0,0,,She said that far to the west,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.13,0:12:46.18,Default,,0,0,0,,in a land across the sea \Nwhere ordinary people cannot reach,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.64,0:12:51.35,Default,,0,0,0,,there lies a paradise where the hero Artorius lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.40,0:13:03.11,Default,,0,0,0,,A paradise, where peace, \Nprosperity and eternal life is promised.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.78,0:13:11.04,Default,,0,0,0,,The hero is still there now, healing his battle wounds.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.79,0:13:18.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Someday, he will come \Nleading an army to slay the savages
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.75,0:13:21.00,Default,,0,0,0,,and conquer the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.13,0:13:26.13,Default,,0,0,0,,My mother's family kept waiting for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.85,0:13:31.77,Default,,0,0,0,,They waited for 500 years.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.73,0:13:37.15,Default,,0,0,0,,The hero hasn't appeared yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.07,0:13:43.74,Default,,0,0,0,,But just think about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.82,0:13:48.49,Default,,0,0,0,,If our ancestor really was living in such a nice place,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.57,0:13:51.74,Default,,0,0,0,,he'd never choose to come back to a world like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.00,0:14:02.67,Default,,0,0,0,,When I was 11, my mother's heart finally snapped.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.85,0:14:12.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Mother!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.28,0:14:29.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Of all the things that could happen, \Nshe thought that my father, who was just passing by,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.82,0:14:32.66,Default,,0,0,0,,was the hero Artorius.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.13,0:14:49.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I realized in an instant.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.76,0:14:54.47,Default,,0,0,0,,If Artorius wasn't going to \Ncome save my mother in that moment,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.56,0:14:57.43,Default,,0,0,0,,then he's never going to come.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.56,0:15:00.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you understand, kids?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.81,0:15:04.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone must do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.32,0:15:08.03,Default,,0,0,0,,A person, not a hero, and not a god.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.29,0:15:25.34,Default,,0,0,0,,It's weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.42,0:15:29.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I had never used a sword before \Nbut it felt right in my hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.97,0:15:32.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew how to swing it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.55,0:15:38.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought of it as proof that I had the blood of \Nthat damn bastard flowing through my veins.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.77,0:15:40.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so ashamed.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.81,0:15:42.85,Default,,0,0,0,,It makes me want to cry.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.28,0:15:57.12,Default,,0,0,0,,You.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.20,0:15:59.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you her child?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.79,0:16:05.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you my child?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.05,0:16:09.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.35,0:16:22.48,Default,,0,0,0,,You have potential.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.56,0:16:24.35,Default,,0,0,0,,You live in the hall starting today.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.48,0:16:31.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew he wasn't someone who an 11-year-old could kill.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.90,0:16:37.20,Default,,0,0,0,,But I succeeded in getting my father to notice me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.49,0:16:42.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I behaved myself in the hall.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.12,0:16:45.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't slack off in my training \Nfor the military arts or horsemanship.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.67,0:16:48.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I even got along well with my half-brothers.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.68,0:16:58.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Good job, Askeladd.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.72,0:17:03.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I always made sure I showed respect to my father.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.66,0:17:22.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I was a loyal son and didn't forget \Nthat he saved me from my life as a slave.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.83,0:17:28.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Before long, everyone \Nstarted to accept me as my father's son.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.34,0:17:36.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I worked on it for two years.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.52,0:17:54.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I was after two things.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.11,0:17:57.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanted to catch him with his guard down, \Nand I wanted the right to inherit his property.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.37,0:18:05.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I wish you could have seen it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.50,0:18:08.29,Default,,0,0,0,,His face had this look, like he was asking, "Why?"
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.05,0:18:16.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I used my brother's sword.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.59,0:18:19.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I chose someone who didn't \Nget along with my father and stole his sword.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.01,0:18:26.68,Default,,0,0,0,,My other brothers thought \Nhe was the one who did it and hanged him.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.77,0:18:29.10,Default,,0,0,0,,They're so simple-minded.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.02,0:18:33.11,Default,,0,0,0,,They're stupid and filthy.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.19,0:18:36.69,Default,,0,0,0,,The have nothing except for their own greed.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.03,0:18:43.95,Default,,0,0,0,,People without beauty like them \Nstarted popping up everywhere
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.04,0:18:46.29,Default,,0,0,0,,and throwing their weight around.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.37,0:18:48.67,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no end to it, no matter how many I kill.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.92,0:18:55.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't care whether it's Artorius, Ragnarok, \Nor the Last Judgment.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.21,0:18:58.51,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're really going to come, \Nthen you'd better hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.97,0:19:06.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, when that happens, I bet they're not going to \Nlet me keep on living either though.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.89,0:19:13.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, that was a long story. Anyway, Thorfinn...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.98,0:19:19.11,Default,,0,0,0,,you still can't even kill me \Neven though it's been 10 years.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.20,0:19:21.24,Default,,0,0,0,,That means you're an idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.58,0:19:27.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.25,0:19:28.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.37,0:19:30.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to kill you, no matter what happens!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.71,0:19:33.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to kill you, no matter what!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.05,0:19:41.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.59,0:19:44.89,Default,,0,0,0,,You're still saying that? Right after what I told you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.56,0:19:50.14,Default,,0,0,0,,You're just like a dog chasing after food.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.52,0:19:56.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I really am thankful for all your hard work.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.44,0:20:00.11,Default,,0,0,0,,All I have to do is put on an act \Nhaving these duels with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.19,0:20:03.91,Default,,0,0,0,,And then you'd go run off \Nand even fight someone like Thorkell.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.33,0:20:08.49,Default,,0,0,0,,You're a useful kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.96,0:20:12.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Unbelievable.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.54,0:20:17.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I must thank Thors, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.31,0:20:28.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.14,0:20:31.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.73,0:20:32.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.06,0:20:37.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up! Shut up! Shut up! Be quiet!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.73,0:20:39.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Now is the time to heal your wounds.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.49,0:20:41.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I said wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.28,0:20:46.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Won't you stop?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.41,0:20:56.58,Default,,0,0,0,,How pathetic.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.96,0:21:03.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, dear. You're stiff now, Bjorn.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.27,0:21:15.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Why me?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.40,0:21:22.69,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the hero's descendant, Askeladd.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.78,0:21:23.90,Default,,0,0,0,,And you're quick-witted.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.20,0:21:29.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you want to become the king yourself \Nand change the world?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.75,0:21:34.75,Default,,0,0,0,,You're joking, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.83,0:21:36.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Weren't you listening just now?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.38,0:21:43.72,Default,,0,0,0,,You're more suited to be the king.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.76,0:21:46.88,Default,,0,0,0,,More than me or King Sweyn.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.05,0:21:50.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I can tell by looking at your face.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.98,0:21:57.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm just a Viking.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.31,0:01:03.43,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,すまん！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.52,0:01:06.15,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,急所を外しちまった！すぐ楽に…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.23,0:01:08.61,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,アシェ…ラッド…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.27,0:01:12.82,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,アンタと…！友達にっ…！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.53,0:01:20.37,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ああ…ビョルン…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.33,0:01:22.70,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,お前は…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.75,0:01:25.79,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,オレのたったひとりの…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.08,0:01:28.21,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,友達だ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.64,0:01:41.01,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,送って…くれ…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.70,0:02:04.04,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,さて…待たせたな小僧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.33,0:02:06.50,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,来い
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.59,0:02:13.09,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,遊んでやる
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.37,0:04:09.91,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,クソ…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.00,0:04:11.54,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,いつもとは違うな…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.88,0:04:18.80,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,で？どっちが勝つと思うね王子？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.88,0:04:20.71,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,賭けるかい？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.80,0:04:22.76,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,どちらでもかまわぬ。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.84,0:04:24.84,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,どちらも死なぬうちに止める
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.47,0:04:27.76,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,つまんねェこと言うなよ。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.01,0:04:32.89,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,こんな手練れ同士の決闘、そうそう拝めるものじゃねンだぜ？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.10,0:04:38.86,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,では…そなたはどちらが強いと考える
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.78,0:04:43.36,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,オレ？ん～そうね…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.45,0:04:48.08,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,アシェラッドかな。ヤツに銀1ポンド！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.16,0:04:50.66,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,賭けぬぞ。なぜそう思う
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.91,0:04:55.42,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,なんとなく？フンイキ？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.46,0:04:59.63,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,トルフィンはそなたに勝ったのであろう。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.71,0:05:01.67,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,アシェラッドはそれ以上か？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.76,0:05:05.34,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,てめェ王子…ナメてんな？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.43,0:05:11.18,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,3人の中でこのオレ様が一番弱ェとか。ありえねェだろうが。あァ？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.60,0:05:17.73,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,強ェの弱ェのってなァ、そんな単純なもんじゃねェのよ。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.81,0:05:22.36,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,勝ったり負けたり、簡単に順序がつかねェのが面白ェんだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.11,0:05:25.11,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,興味ない
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.20,0:05:27.91,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,てめェやっぱ女だろ？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.87,0:05:33.62,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,どうしたトルフィン？来いよ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.66,0:05:37.00,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,降りが強くなる前に終わらせてェ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.96,0:05:45.80,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,しょうがねぇなァ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.52,0:05:56.39,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ホレ！攻めやすくなったろ？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.77,0:06:00.81,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,来い…坊主
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.83,0:06:17.83,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,な？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.50,0:06:25.17,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,まだわかんねェのか？なんでこうなるのか
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.02,0:06:45.53,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,さっきの訂正。勝負になってねェやこりゃ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.61,0:06:49.95,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,トルフィンの奴、クセから何からアシェラッドに見抜かれてら。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.12,0:06:54.91,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,この2人相当やってんな。決闘の理由は？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.99,0:06:58.46,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,知らぬ。聞いていない
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.46,0:07:05.13,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ったく…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.21,0:07:07.26,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,成長のねェガキだ。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.76,0:07:11.34,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,トルケルに勝って調子に乗ったか
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.81,0:07:19.27,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,いいかげんうんざりするぜ…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.60,0:07:23.44,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,やめよ！そこまでだ！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.32,0:07:30.45,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,片手でこのオレに勝てると思ったか
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.49,0:07:36.20,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,まったく…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.29,0:07:39.12,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,今日はクソ気分のいい日だぜ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.12,0:07:41.29,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,やめろ！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.63,0:07:52.26,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,もうよせ！気絶している！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.34,0:07:53.93,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,そなたの勝ちだ！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.01,0:07:58.52,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あーあ。ホントに止めやがんの
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.60,0:08:01.14,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,トルフィン！おい！トルフィン！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.23,0:08:12.74,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,わかるか？決闘はもう終わったぞ。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.82,0:08:14.45,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,そなたの負けだ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.45,0:08:22.04,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,よせ。もう終わりだ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.12,0:08:23.29,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,てめえェ…！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.37,0:08:25.79,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,気を失ったのだ。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.88,0:08:27.54,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,すでにとどめを刺されている。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.63,0:08:34.30,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,右腕が治ってから、またやり直せ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.64,0:08:39.89,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,治っても同じですよ。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.97,0:08:42.02,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ケガのせいじゃねェ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.10,0:08:44.69,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,そのバカはバカだから負ける。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.48,0:08:49.19,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ふだんはちったァ考えて戦うようになってきちゃいるが…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.48,0:08:54.32,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,いっぺん頭に血が上ったら全部台なしだ。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.45,0:08:59.62,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,首筋を狙ってるのが目線で丸わかりなんだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.04,0:09:06.79,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,すぐにブチ切れて…でけェ声だして。
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.88,0:09:10.13,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,得物振り回すのァバカの戦だ。
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.21,0:09:12.80,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,まったくどいつもこいつも…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.88,0:09:15.13,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,美しさのかけらもありゃしねェ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.72,0:09:19.43,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ビョルンの言うとおりさ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.51,0:09:22.02,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,オレァ戦士ってのが大嫌いだ。
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.31,0:09:27.06,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ノルド戦士…ヴァイキングは特にな
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.02,0:09:33.74,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,初めて殺した相手もノルド戦士だった。
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.82,0:09:36.36,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,美しくない男だったぜ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.91,0:09:42.66,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,オレの親父だ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.37,0:09:47.25,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,小僧…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.33,0:09:49.92,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,後学のために教えてやろう
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.25,0:09:55.30,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,憎い相手の殺し方をな
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.48,0:10:10.36,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,よいしょー！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.44,0:10:12.90,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ガタきてんなァ\N後ろ気ぃつけェ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.53,0:10:20.99,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,オレは…奴隷の母親から産まれた。
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.83,0:10:28.50,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,お袋は病気で働くことができなかった
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.54,0:10:32.84,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,なんで物心つく頃にゃ、
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.92,0:10:35.46,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,鍛冶場や厩の下働きだった
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.93,0:10:41.43,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,体はいつも灰や煤や
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.51,0:10:46.02,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,馬のクソやらで白かったり黒かったりでな。
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.10,0:10:48.10,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ついたアダ名が“アシェラッド”
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.19,0:10:52.19,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,“灰まみれ”って意味だ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.65,0:10:56.69,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ウォラフ様が帰っていらしたぞー！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.78,0:10:59.70,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,また大勝利だとよぉ！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.91,0:11:08.71,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,親父はユトランドの豪族だった
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.79,0:11:12.29,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ウォラフ様ー！！\Nおかえりなさいウォラフ様！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.38,0:11:15.71,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,酒と女と殺しが好きな…まァ、
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.80,0:11:18.22,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,どこにでもいるようなヴァイキングだ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.38,0:11:24.05,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,オレみたいなガキを、あちこちの女に産ませてたらしいが
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.14,0:11:28.85,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,名を与えたのは本妻の産んだ、年長の子供たちだけだった
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.94,0:11:36.48,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,それ以外のガキなんざ…顔も覚えちゃいなかっただろうぜ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.95,0:11:42.49,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,お袋は若い頃、
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.57,0:11:45.87,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,親父のお気に入りの奴隷だったそうだが
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.95,0:11:50.87,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,病を得てからは、犬と同じ扱いだった
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.21,0:11:55.88,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,生きることがつらいのはオレにとっちゃ当たり前のことだったが
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.96,0:11:59.05,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,どうやら、お袋は違ったようだ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.22,0:12:08.64,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,お袋はよく、先祖の英雄アルトリウスの話をした。
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.72,0:12:11.44,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,同じ話を何度もした。
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.15,0:12:15.90,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,500年前、蛮族の侵入から
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.98,0:12:19.44,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,お袋の故郷を守った将軍の伝説だ。
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.49,0:12:25.53,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,お袋は英雄復活の伝説を信じていた
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.62,0:12:31.08,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,自分を病や奴隷身分から解き放ってくれる者の再来をな…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.96,0:12:36.25,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あんまり繰り返すもんだからよ。
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.33,0:12:38.34,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,オレも信じるようになった
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.63,0:12:42.05,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,はるか西の彼方…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.13,0:12:46.18,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,常人にはたどりつくことのできない彼岸の地に、
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.64,0:12:51.35,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,英雄アルトリウスの住む楽土があるという
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.40,0:13:03.11,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,平和と豊穣、不老不死が約束された理想郷だ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.78,0:13:11.04,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,英雄はそこで、今も戦の傷を癒やしているらしい。
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.79,0:13:18.67,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,いつの日か彼は万軍を従え来て、蛮族どもを誅し、
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.75,0:13:21.00,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,この世を平定して下さる。
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.13,0:13:26.13,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,お袋の一族は…それを待ち続けた。
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.85,0:13:31.77,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,待ちに待って500年。
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.73,0:13:37.15,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,英雄はまだ現れない
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.07,0:13:43.74,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,だが考えてもみろよ。
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.82,0:13:48.49,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,もし本当にご先祖様がそんないい所に暮らしてるならよ。
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.57,0:13:51.74,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,すき好んでこんな世界に帰ってくるわきゃアねェ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.00,0:14:02.67,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,そして…オレが11の時ついにお袋の心が折れた
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.85,0:14:12.85,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,母さん！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.28,0:14:29.74,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,よりにもよって…たまたま通りかかった親父のことを、
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.82,0:14:32.66,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,英雄アルトリウスと勘違いしたらしい
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.13,0:14:49.09,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,一瞬で悟った。
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.76,0:14:54.47,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,今この時アルトリウスがお袋を助けに来ないのなら、
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.56,0:14:57.43,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,そんな者は永遠に来ないのだと
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.56,0:15:00.73,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,わかるか若造ども。
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.81,0:15:04.23,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,誰かがやらねばならん。
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.32,0:15:08.03,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,英雄でも神でもねェ。誰かがな
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.29,0:15:25.34,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,不思議なもんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.42,0:15:29.88,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,初めて使ったのに、剣はオレの手によくなじんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.97,0:15:32.22,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,どう振ればいいのか、わかっていた
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.55,0:15:38.68,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,オレの体に目の前のクソ野郎の血が流れている証拠だと思った
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.77,0:15:40.73,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,情けねェ話さ。
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.81,0:15:42.85,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,涙が出るぜ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.28,0:15:57.12,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,お前…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.20,0:15:59.41,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,その女の子か
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.79,0:16:05.67,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ワシの子か？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.05,0:16:09.21,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,そうです
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.35,0:16:22.48,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,見込みがある。
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.56,0:16:24.35,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,今日から館に住め
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.48,0:16:31.53,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,さすがに11歳のガキに殺れる相手とは思ってなかった。
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.90,0:16:37.20,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,まずは親父の目にとまること。成功だ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.49,0:16:42.04,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,館では行儀よくしていたよ。
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.12,0:16:45.58,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,武術や馬術の鍛錬を怠らなかった。
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.67,0:16:48.96,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,腹違いの兄貴たちとも、うまくやってた
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.72,0:17:03.48,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,いつも親父を立てるように気を遣ってな
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.66,0:17:22.75,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,奴隷暮らしから救ってくれた恩を決して忘れない忠実な息子だった
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.83,0:17:28.96,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,じきに周りも身内も、\Nすっかりオレを親父の子として受け入れるようになった
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.34,0:17:36.05,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,この作業に2年をかけたぜ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.52,0:17:54.03,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,狙いは2つ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.11,0:17:57.91,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,親父の油断と、遺産の相続権だ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.37,0:18:05.41,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,お前らにも見せてやりたかったよ。
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.50,0:18:08.29,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,親父のあの“何故！？”ってツラ…！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.05,0:18:16.51,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,使ったのは兄貴の剣だ。
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.59,0:18:19.84,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,親父と仲の悪い奴から選んで盗んだ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.01,0:18:26.68,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,他の兄貴たちは犯人と思い込んで、そいつをリンチにかけちまいやんの。
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.77,0:18:29.10,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,全く単純な奴らだぜ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.02,0:18:33.11,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,バカで不潔で…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.19,0:18:36.69,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,テメェの欲望以外に何もねェクソどもさ。
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.03,0:18:43.95,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ああいう美しくねェ奴らが、そこら中からわいて出てきて
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.04,0:18:46.29,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,幅を利かせやがる。
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.37,0:18:48.67,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,いくらブチ殺してもキリがねェ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.92,0:18:55.13,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,アルトリウスでもラグナロクでも、最後の審判でも何でもいいからよ。
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.21,0:18:58.51,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,マジに来るなら、急いでもらいたいもんだぜ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.97,0:19:06.14,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ま。そん時ゃオレも…生きちゃいられねェだろうがな
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.89,0:19:13.82,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ああ長くなったな。要するにだトルフィン
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.98,0:19:19.11,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,10年以上かけてオレひとり倒せないお前は…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.20,0:19:21.24,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ボンクラだって話さ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.58,0:19:27.16,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,うるせぇ！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.25,0:19:28.29,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,オレは！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.37,0:19:30.79,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,オレは何があってもテメェを殺す！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.71,0:19:33.59,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ぜってぇ殺してやる！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.05,0:19:41.26,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ったく…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.59,0:19:44.89,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,言ってるそばからそれかよ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.56,0:19:50.14,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,犬みてェに餌につられて駆け回りやがって…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.52,0:19:56.36,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,おめぇの働きにゃあマジで頭が下がるよ。
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.44,0:20:00.11,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,茶番みてェな決闘につきあってやるだけで、
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.19,0:20:03.91,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あのトルケルにまでホイホイ挑んでいくんだもんなぁ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.33,0:20:08.49,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,便利なガキだよ。お前は
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.96,0:20:12.96,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,まったく…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.54,0:20:17.67,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,トールズにも感謝しねェとな
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.31,0:20:28.56,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,待て…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.14,0:20:31.64,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,待て…！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.73,0:20:32.98,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,もうよせ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.06,0:20:37.65,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,うるせぇ！うるせぇ！うるせえぇっ！！黙れえぇっ！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.73,0:20:39.32,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,今は傷を癒やせ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.49,0:20:41.95,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ちやがれ…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.28,0:20:46.37,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,よさぬか！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.41,0:20:56.58,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,はぁーあ！なっさけね…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.96,0:21:03.97,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,やれやれ。すっかり固くなっちまったなビョルン
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.27,0:21:15.69,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,何故…私なのだ。
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.40,0:21:22.69,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,英雄の末裔はそなたであろう。アシェラッド。
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.78,0:21:23.90,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,才気もある。
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.20,0:21:29.62,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,己自身が王となり、世を変えようとは思わぬのか？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.75,0:21:34.75,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ご冗談でしょ。
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.83,0:21:36.87,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,話聞いてなかったんですか？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.38,0:21:43.72,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あなたのほうが王にふさわしい。
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.76,0:21:46.88,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,オレやスヴェン王よりもね
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.05,0:21:50.39,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,顔見りゃわかります
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.98,0:21:57.06,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,オレァただのヴァイキングですよ
